Package com.fortify.pub.bugtracker.plugin

Base interfaces and classes that represent a bug tracker plugin.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BatchBugTrackerPlugin  
    BugTrackerPlugin
    Interface that Bug Tracker plugins must implement.
    ChangesetDiscoveryPlugin Deprecated
    InterruptableBugtracker  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBatchBugTrackerPlugin
    This is the abstract class from which all plugins implementing BatchBugTrackerPlugin would extend.
    AbstractBugTrackerAndChangesetDiscoveryPlugin Deprecated
    Instead of implementing this interface, plugin can calculate candidate changesets before filing the bug using fields in BugSubmission.getIssueDetail(), namely getLastBuildWithoutIssue(), getFileName() and getDetectedInBuild()
    AbstractBugTrackerPlugin
    This is the abstract class from which all plugins implementing BugTrackerPlugin would extend.
    BugTrackerPluginHelper
    Class with utility methods that bug tracker plugins can use.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    BugTrackerPluginImplementation
    Use this annotation to mark bug tracker plugin implementation classes.
